OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fwill continue to bring showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain overnight, and some
OL,8,Ffog over the hills too. Staying frost
OL,9,Ffree under the blanket of cloud with
OL,10,Flight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA cloudy and grey start with
OL,13,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain. Skies
OL,14,Fwill brighten in the south later with
OL,15,Fsome hazy spells of sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
